ZH: 这个监狱看守了十年，他终于能够提前获得假释。
EN: After ten years of being a prison guard, he is finally able to get early parole.

ZH: 作为一名看守，他必须保证囚犯们遵守规矩。
EN: As a prison warden, he must ensure that the prisoners follow the rules.

