EN: They lock the prisoners in the cells, under the continuous supervision of the prison guards.

ZH: 他负责看守这家店铺，确保没有人在关门后侵入。
EN: He is responsible for guarding this shop and making sure no one breaks in after closing.

ZH: 监狱看守严禁携带任何违禁品。
EN: The prison guards strictly prohibit carrying any prohibited items.

